docs.snippet: The City of New-York offers a most remarkable example of the indifference which communities, as well as individuals, often manifest for the privileges which Fortune has bestowed upon them. No city was ever blessed with such splendid facilities for...
docs.lead_paragraph: The City of New-York offers a most remarkable example of the indifference which communities, as well as individuals, often manifest for the privileges which Fortune has bestowed upon them. No city was ever blessed with such splendid facilities for cleanliness, in an abundant supply of water, as New-York is.

docs.snippet: The city is dull, and there is very little important business transacted by the Cabinet, inasmuch as the Secretary of State, the Attorney-General, and the Secretary of the Navy are all absent in search of a change of air and recruited health.

docs.lead_paragraph: HEALTH COMMISSIONERS.--The Board met on Saturday. Present, the Mayor, Messrs. CLANCY, HASWELL, DIS. ROCKWELL, THOMPSON and MILLER. Charleston was declared to be an infected port. The schooner T. D. Wagner arrived here Aug. 20 Ordered that her cotton be discharged on barge at Quarantine for ventilation,
